    "title": "Digital Marketing Manager Vacancy at Myntra - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Myntra. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Raipur-based team.\n\nAbout Myntra:\nMyntra is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Magento\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in WooCommerce\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Myntra!",
